{
  "stem": "21582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took us then to umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they loaded us into the freight trains, box trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know if they were cattle trains, but they certainly looked like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And at this umschlagplatz, you had this little remainder of-- of-- of the community in such fright.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you know, I-- I remember when we walked into the-- when they-- when they pushed us, and-- and of course whips, and-- and-- and insults, and slaps, and kicks, and-- and shouts, [SPEAKING GERMAN] which means waste.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were pushed into the freight cars, and I remember looking out of the freight cars, the-- the the sounds, the-- the sights, and-- and-- and the flames were just so enormous.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It-- it was just-- it was-- and-- there was a-- a prism of-- of hues, of-- of the fires that went all the way up from the ground and just into the sky.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In a way, it-- it-- it was-- it was not like-- like reality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't think you could capture it on a movie, these flames licking the skies, and-- and the smoke, every-- every hue, every range of color.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there they shut us into-- into-- into the freight cars very dense, choking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Our lips were parched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they were shooting, shooting into the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I remember how we clung to my mother and father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The three of us clung to one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And those who survived the shooting into the cars were dumped off in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And-- and-- and all that was left of Warsaw was a big graveyard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "A smoldering graveyard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the train, there was blood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people wounded, the people screaming, people sitting in absolute silence, actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
